title: (feat/angular2) Made the first version of admin page
message:
(feat/angular2) Made the first version of admin page

server/admin/app
- main.ts: entry point of app
- app.component.ts: main app
- custom-date.pipe.ts: custom pipe for converting date
- custom-datetime.pipe.ts: custom pipe for converting date and time
server/admin/app/deal
- deal.ts: interface for deal data structure
- deals.component.ts: for listing deals data
- deal-details.component.ts: for showing individual deal data
server/admin/app/hotel
- hotel.ts: interface for hotel data structure
- hotels.component.ts: for listing hotels data
- hotel-details.component.ts: for showing individual hotel data
server/admin/app/client
- client.ts: interface for client data structure
- clients.component.ts: for listing clients data
- client-details.component.ts: for showing individual client data
server/admin/app/contract
- contract.ts: interface for contract data structure
- contracts.component.ts: for listing contract data
- contract-details.component.ts: for showing individual contract data
server/admin/app/services
- deals.service.ts: http request for getting deals and deal data
- hotels.service.ts: http request for getting hotels and hotel data
